727262f-a.title: Queens: Little Neck Parkway - 74th Avenue
727262f-a.text:
Little Neck Parkway, west side, near 74th Avenue,
showing the Henry Cox (Cocks) house of 1873-1891. lIn
1891 the farm contained 104 acres and stretched north from
Motor Parkway from where views 2 and 3 were taken.
View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection 1922
MAY BE REPRODUCED
Views, 2,3r P.L. Sperr
NO REIRODCTIONS  March 1, 1927
